$interpreted: Jahan: My god, you scared the living hell out of me. How do you not make a single noise when you walk!
Bandit: It's part of my skill set...

Jahan: Hmm, good point. You're the most famous thief in the entire kingdom. 

If you made noise when you walked, you wouldn't be able to sneak into a noble's mansion.
Jahan: How did it go? Everything done?
Bandit: Ask me to steal the Vincent family's token of loyalty, then told me to put it right back. I have no idea what you are doing but...
Bandit: Damn it... I did your dirty work, now you plan to get rid of me?
Jahan: M-Mister thief, this is a misunderstanding...I was just...
Jahan: Mister! Mister! Please have mercy! I have parents to feed and grandparents to take care of.
Jahan: If I die, there will be no one left to take care of them.
Bandit: That's none of my business!
Jahan: I mean, you're the best thief in the entire kingdom. Did you not realize that I didn't really mean to kill you back there?
Jahan: Whew, good thing I applied poison to the weapon. Took longer than expected...that was close.
Jahan: Almost forgot. Since you've no use for this...might as well take it back.
